{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuItem\/setActionAndTargetValue(action:targetValue:)"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets or unsets the “action” and “target” attributes of "},{"code":"menuItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"setActionAndTargetValue","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"action"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar","text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetValue","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"action","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then both the “action” and “target” attributes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"are unset (and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"targetValue"},{"type":"text","text":" is ignored)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"action"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the “action” attribute is set.  The"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“target” attribute is then set to the value of ","type":"text"},{"code":"targetValue","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if it is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"non-"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or unset otherwise."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Normal menu items (ie: not submenu, section or other custom item","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"types) are expected to have the “action” attribute set to identify"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the action that they are associated with.  The state type of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"action help to determine the disposition of the menu item.  See"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action","isActive":true},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","isActive":true},{"text":" for an overview of actions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In general, clicking on the menu item will result in activation of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the named action with the “target” attribute given as the parameter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to the action invocation.  If the “target” attribute is not set then","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the action is invoked with no parameter."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the action has no state then the menu item is usually drawn as a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"plain menu item (ie: with no additional decoration).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the action has a boolean state then the menu item is usually drawn"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as a toggle menu item (ie: with a checkmark or equivalent"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"indication).  The item should be marked as ‘toggled’ or ‘checked’"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when the boolean state is ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the action has a string state then the menu item is usually drawn"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as a radio menu item (ie: with a radio bullet or equivalent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"indication).  The item should be marked as ‘selected’ when the string","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"state is equal to the value of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"code":"g_menu_item_set_action_and_target()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_menu_item_set_detailed_action()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for two equivalent calls that are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"probably more convenient for most uses."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menuitem\/setactionandtargetvalue(action:targetvalue:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","title":"setActionAndTargetValue(action:targetValue:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO16MenuItemProtocolPAAE23setActionAndTargetValue6action06targetI0ySPys4Int8VGSg_4GLib10VariantRefVSgtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO8MenuItemC","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"setActionAndTargetValue","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"action","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"text":">?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"external